You were saying, comrade?

101
00:51:43,000 --> 00:51:44,600
Shut up!

102
01:03:29,100 --> 01:03:30,100
Help. . .

103
01:03:30,650 --> 01:03:32,400
The ``Wolverines`` . . .

104
01:03:32,450 --> 01:03:34,300
. . . are attacking.

105
01:03:34,400 --> 01:03:36,000
Follow me. . .quickly.

106
