Children did this?
                            
107
01:05:07,954 --> 01:05:09,387
It`s rebels.
                            
108
01:05:09,556 --> 01:05:11,023
What rebels?
                            
109
01:05:11,091 --> 01:05:12,749
They`re bandits!
                            
110
01:05:15,762 --> 01:05:19,323
Every time they shoot,
the revolution grows.
                            
111
01:05:19,499 --> 01:05:20,295
I know.
                            
112
01:05:20,467 --> 01:05:21,900
I was a partisan.
                            
113
01:05:22,636 --> 01:05:26,299
And what are you now?
                            
114
01:05:27,407 --> 01:05:29,569
Now I`m like you 

115
01:05:30,600 --> 01:05:31,400
