of pacification is growing.

121
01:17:49,649 --> 01:17:51,947
These are the tactics of the lie.

122
01:17:52,351 --> 01:17:55,479
Lies have the stench
of death and defeat.

123
01:17:58,357 --> 01:18:04,489
You can only win a war by exterminating
the enemy.

124
01:18:06,232 --> 01:18:08,723
Do you know who we are fighting?

125
01:18:11,237 --> 01:18:14,000
We are fighting Wolverines.

126
01:18:15,500 --> 01:18:18,500
Small, ferocious animals.

127
01:18:19,512 --> 01:18:22,140
For them, you need a hunter.

128
01:18:22,815 --> 01:18:27,445
And you know. . .I am a hunter.

129
01:18:32,425 --> 01:18:34,484
From this moment on there

130
01:18:34,660 --> 01:18:39,495
will be no further reprisals
against civilians.

131
01:18:39,665 --> 01:18:41,724
This was stupid.

132
01:18:44,303 --> 01:18:46,396
Impotence.

133
01:18:49,775 --> 01:18:51,208
Comrades

134
